name: Lilith`s Laughter
description: Mother of Demons and Queen of Witchcraft, a fatal seducer, wearing a sharp crescent moon in her hair, with a burning emerald gaze, demonic Feminine, a vampire and the Night itself, beautiful and dangerous, is full of strength. Knowing everyone who rules in Chaos, in the East, in the West, appearing in all corners of the universe and in all pagan legends of mankind, with skin the color of a thundercloud and a peacock feather - a symbol of the Devil - the King. In her smile, the triumph of the temptress and the mockery of the trickster, the horns are casually adorned with jewels, Sumer, Egypt, Iran, Syria, Kali, Shiva ... Lilith is huge and the co-plant on her shoulder emphasizes this with its disproportionately small size. Behind her is a blood-fiery background.
